es</span><hr size=1> <br>Many of you seem to be overlooking the fact that wood elf rangers also have hide.  Obviously we don't do it as well as rogues, but it is very effective for clearing your opponents target.<br><br>To be honest, a competent ranger vs. a competent rogue of similar levels will generally result in a ranger victory.  There's just to many ways to inhibit the rogue, whilst the rogue only has a few tricks.  And that list is cut in half if the ranger has see invis (which we get at 39).<br><br>No disrespect to rogues, but you're not going to beat a competent ranger in PvP.  And just run if they are post 51 and have a good bow.  Post 55?  You wont have time to run.<br><br>lab <p><img src="http://moresoda.com/images/josh/eqsig1.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=23918.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showMessageRange?topicID=23918.topic&start=41&stop=45>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showPrevMessage?topicID=23918.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showNextMessage?topicID=23918.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=23918.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion.emailToFriend?topicID=23918.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesa